						               													<description>This game was attached to the ioGioco 18 magazine.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Finally the Ork Pistols concert tonight! In the Casbah, the coolest rock cave of the Desolate Lands, the punk-ork clans are ready to throw themselves under the concert stage in a frenzied Pogo, by dint of jumps, chases and shoves.&amp;#10;Will you be able to make your clan conquer the best places and keep its members as united as possible, according to the motto of &amp;ldquo;If the kids are united&amp;hellip; then we'll never be divided&amp;rdquo;?&amp;#10;The evening promises to be very, very&amp;hellip; eventful!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this game, the results of the dice are used to make the members of our rocker orc clan reach the best positions. And eventually to displace rival orcs.&amp;#10;There are two sets of dice. One represents the entry queue. The other set, called &amp;quot;the reserve&amp;quot;, is used to choose which die to take from the queue and use for our placement. Then rearrange the queue with the die taken from the reserve.&amp;#10;If you don't have 6 pairs of dice of the same color, there are tiles and rules in the magazine for using only 6 dice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
